@startuml
title Siemens U273 Plugin - Component Overview

skinparam componentStyle rectangle

actor "DAW Host" as Host

package "U273 Plugin Binary\nVST3 / AU via JUCE" {
  [PluginProcessor\nJUCE AudioProcessor] as Processor
  [PluginEditor\nJUCE UI] as Editor
  [ParameterBridge] as ParameterBridge
  [PresetManager] as PresetManager
  [MeterBridge] as MeterBridge
  [Realtime DSP Engine] as DSP
  [U273 Core\nmath / units / tables] as Core
}

package "Offline / Validation" {
  [Scientific Reference Engine\nMNA / golden comparison] as Reference
  database "Golden Files\nJS DC/AC/transient" as Golden
}

Host --> Processor : prepare/process/state
Host --> Editor : open editor / user input

Editor --> ParameterBridge : parameter edits
Editor --> MeterBridge : read meters
Processor --> ParameterBridge : read published snapshot
Processor --> PresetManager : get/set state
Processor --> DSP : prepare/process/reset
DSP --> Core : constants, math, tables
ParameterBridge --> Core : ranges, units
PresetManager --> ParameterBridge : restore/migrate state
MeterBridge <-- DSP : publish bounded meter values

Reference --> Core : shared units/constants
Reference --> Golden : read expected results
Reference ..> DSP : offline regression only

note right of DSP
Realtime constraints:
- no allocation
- no locks
- no logging
- no file/network I/O
- bounded execution
end note

note bottom of Reference
Offline only.
May allocate and solve MNA/Newton.
Never called by processBlock.
end note

@enduml

